reviewText: My five year old Grand Daughter loves it and plays it all the time. was unable to fine it any where else.

I bought this for my 20 month old granddaughter and my daughter tells me that she absolutely loves all the Rolie Polie videos.  She loves the fast paced storylines and it keeps her interest.  I enjoyed watching this when it was a television show when my daughters were little and thought it would be perfect for my granddaughter.  Boy was I right!
